Contributor.Organization: CHU Ste-Justine Research Center/Université de Montréal

Sample.Title: Placenta Ctrl 1 Capture

Channel.Extract-Protocol: Genomic DNA was extracted using QIAamp DNA Micro Kit (Qiagen) following manufacturer's recommendations Libraries were performed using SureSelectXT Methyl-Seq mouse Target Enrichment System (Agilent) following manufacturer's protocol

Sample.Data-Processing: Sequence reads were trimmed using Trimmomatic (v0.36) Alignment and methylation counts were performed with Bismark (v0.18.1) Assembly: mm10 Supplementary files format and content: tab-delimited files including CpG sites coordinate, coverage, methylation values Supplementary files format and content: Input files for the methylKit package

Sample.Title: Placenta Ctrl 1 mRNA-Seq

Channel.Extract-Protocol: RNA was extracted using Qiagen Rneasy Mini kit (Qiagen) following manufacturer's recommendations Libraries were performed using NEBNext Ultra II Directional RNA Library Prep Kit following manufacturer's protocol

Sample.Data-Processing: Sequence reads were trimmed using Trimmomatic (v0.36) Gene counts matrix and differentially expressed genes (DEGs) were obtained using the R package DESeq2 (v1.24.0) Assembly: mm10 Supplementary files format and content: tab-delimited text files including raw counts
